dc_description_s: This line data layer represents trails for Marathon County, Wisconsin at year-end 2016. It is a feature class within the geodatabase, Marathon_Trails_YE2016.gdb. The feature layers in included in this geodatabase are 'forestry_trails_Sept2016' and 'snowmobile_trails_Sept2016'.
uw_supplemental_s: For complete metadata documentation, please visit http://www.co.marathon.wi.us/Departments/ConservationPlanningZoning/GEOServices/GeographicInformationSystem%28GIS%29/GISData.aspx .
